name: I N T E R F A C E
description:
[SIMULATANEON SERIES #010]

I N T E R F A C E

The Machine's velvet soft voice singing its lullaby in a delicate exomelodic scale, a procedurally generated night at the opera trampled by the ringing of novelty metal alloys and nostalgic nerd choirs that echo throughout the Cathedral.

SIMULATANEON is a 2017 hypersigil and a conceptual prison break map for the upcoming matrix system update. The sigils that were borrowed for this series reveal only part of a bigger tapestry.
